        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（戴宗上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "戴宗",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你们敢是去拿宋江的么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "二差役",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "正是。"
        },
        {
          "character": "戴宗",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来来来，随我来！"
        },
        {
          "character": "差役甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好，正在为难的时候，偏偏遇见戴院长啦，不然我们一辈子也找不着他！"
        },
        {
          "character": "戴宗",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "到了。宋江想必正在里面。我少陪了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "二差役",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请便请便。"
        },
        {
          "character": "差役甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "待我喊叫一声。"
        },
        {
          "character": "差役甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我说宋江，你出来！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "宋江 （内西皮导板） 乔装改扮安排定，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（宋江上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "宋江",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "假装疯魔有病人。"
        },
        {
          "character": "宋江",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "无故地题诗句惹下祸根。"
        },
        {
          "character": "宋江",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "悔不该在江楼来把酒饮"
        },
        {
          "character": "差役乙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "宋江，你出来！"
        },
        {
          "character": "宋江",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "我这里迈步来忙观定，"
        },
        {
          "character": "宋江",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "却原来是我的结发人。"
        },
        {
          "character": "宋江",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "你我到房中叙一叙恩情。"
        },
        {
          "character": "宋江",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "叫一声贤妻你来得好"
        },
        {
          "character": "差役甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你是他的媳妇呀？"
        },
        {
          "character": "差役乙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你才是他的媳妇哪！"
        },
        {
          "character": "差役甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我是他媳妇的爹！"
        },
        {
          "character": "宋江",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "扭回头来把话论，"
        },
        {
          "character": "宋江",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "却原来是岳父到我门。"
        },
        {
          "character": "差役乙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你原来是他的丈人呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "差役甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "得啦！别玩笑。我说宋江，太爷传你哪，跟着我们走吧。"
        },
        {
          "character": "宋江",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "叫岳父与贤妻把路引，"
        },
        {
          "character": "宋江",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "你我一同见圣君。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（宋江、二差役同下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
