    {
      "scene_index": 3,
      "label": "第三场",
      "characters_present": [
        "二差役",
        "宋江",
        "州官",
        "差役甲",
        "青袍官甲"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四青袍、州官同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "州官",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "奉了太尊令，审问造反人。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（差役甲上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "差役甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "启太爷：宋江拿到。"
        },
        {
          "character": "青袍官甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "带上来！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（差役乙押宋江同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "宋江",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "我大摇大摆往前进，"
        },
        {
          "character": "宋江",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "上面厢坐的是对头人。"
        },
        {
          "character": "宋江",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "问我一言我答一声。"
        },
        {
          "character": "宋江",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "我撩袍端带上龙庭"
        },
        {
          "character": "州官",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "胆大宋江，见了本州为何不跪？"
        },
        {
          "character": "宋江",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你是何等样人，我岂能跪你！"
        },
        {
          "character": "州官",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你在酒楼题了反诗，你要从实招来！"
        },
        {
          "character": "宋江",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "想我宋江，乃是天神下界。吾奉玉帝敕旨，带领十万天兵天将，去至京城，扫"
        },
        {
          "character": "宋江",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "荡奸臣。我不久就是皇帝了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "宋江",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "我奉上方玉帝令，"
        },
        {
          "character": "宋江",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "带领十万鬼神兵。"
        },
        {
          "character": "宋江",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "一统山河我坐朝廷。"
        },
        {
          "character": "宋江",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "除却朝中众奸佞"
        },
        {
          "character": "州官",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "看宋江，满口疯话，但不知是真是假。呵哈有了：待我将些尿粪臭秽之物，叫"
        },
        {
          "character": "州官",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他去用，若是吃，便是真疯；他若不吃，便是装就。"
        },
        {
          "character": "州官",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来！"
        },
        {
          "character": "二差役",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有！"
        },
        {
          "character": "州官",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "将尿粪抬一桶上来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "二差役",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "嗻！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（二差役同下，抬桶同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "二差役",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "嘿，好臭好臭！"
        },
        {
          "character": "二差役",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "粪抬到。"
        },
        {
          "character": "青袍官甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "宋江，你莫要欺哄本州。堂下有粪水一桶，你去用来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "宋江",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呵哈，哈哈哈！我今到此，你还要费心设宴。好，待我用来。喝喝，我就叨扰"
        },
        {
          "character": "宋江",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "宋江",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "多谢兄台太多情，"
        },
        {
          "character": "宋江",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "来此还要设席珍。"
        },
        {
          "character": "宋江",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "众位何妨同来请"
        },
        {
          "character": "二差役",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这样的好东西，你请吧，我们没有这个造化。"
        },
        {
          "character": "宋江",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "他一个一个就不应声。"
        },
        {
          "character": "宋江",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "他不识海味与山珍。"
        },
        {
          "character": "宋江",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有道是“主不请，客不饮”，你请用啊！"
        },
        {
          "character": "宋江",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "我洒他个满堂乱纷纷！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（宋江向四周泼洒粪水。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "州官",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来！将宋江暂且收禁，待我禀报蔡大老爷，任他发落便了。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众人同下。）"
        }
      ],
